RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT MODULE_ID,MODULE_DESC FROM OLVWS_MODULES WHERE NVL(IN_CLASS_APPLICABLE,'N') = 'Y' ORDER BY MODULE_ID
SELECT EVENT_CODE,EVENT_DESCR FROM OLTBS_EVENT WHERE MODULE = ? AND ALLOW_ASSOCIATION_OF_INTEREST = 'Y' ORDER BY EVENT_CODE

SELECT AMOUNT_TAG, DESCRIPTION FROM OLTBS_AMOUNT_TAG WHERE MODULE = ? AND INTEREST_ALLOWED = 'Y' UNION SELECT DISTINCT DERIVED_TAG, TAG_DESC FROM OLTBS_DERIVED_TAG_MASTER WHERE MODULE = ? ORDER BY AMOUNT_TAG

SELECT RATE_CODE, DESCRIPTION FROM CFTMS_FLOATING_RATE_CODE WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT A.RATE_CODE,A.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER A WHERE A.RECORD_STAT= 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT='A' AND A.TYPE = NVL(?,A.TYPE)
SELECT RATE_CODE,RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE='P' AND RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'
SELECT FIELD_NAME ,FIELD_DESC FROM OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE WHERE MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND FIELD_TYPE = 'A' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY FIELD_NAME
SELECT RULE_ID, DESCRIPTION FROM LFTB_ICCF_RLAVL WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RULE_TYPE = 'I'
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT CLASS_CODE FROM LFTMS_INTEREST_CLASS WHERE MODULE = ?

SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE, B.FIELD_DESC FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE A, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.FIELD_NAME AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND B.FIELD_TYPE = A.RATE_CODE_USAGE AND ? = 'X' AND ? = 'T' UNION SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE='S' AND RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' AND ? <> 'X' OR ? <> 'T'

SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND CCY_CODE NOT IN (SELECT COMPONENT_CCY FROM LFTMS_CLASS_CCY_RATES WHERE MODULE = ? AND CLASS_CODE = ?) UNION SELECT '*.*', 'ALL CURRENCY CODES' FROM DUAL WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LFTMS_CLASS_CCY_RATES WHERE MODULE = ? AND CLASS_CODE = ? AND COMPONENT_CCY = '*.*')
